Package: RERB
Type: Package
Title: Provides wrapper functions to run repertoire analysis on single-cell datasets using the Immcantation pipeline
Version: 0.9.6
Date: 2025-06-09
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Pascal", "Chappert",
